I can add feature upon demand.
I could add a "push bitmap" as a new additional filter, if ever desired.

I could make this into a real bonafide "directshow input capture" source (pseudo-camera) if desired, as well, though some
other products out there also do that and are free for private use, but I could if desired (ping me).
Basically you want a feature, ping me, you got it.

blttest is originally from http://stereopsis.com/blttest and measure bitblt speed 
(which is quite hardware dependent, or so I'm told).